<i>ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh</i> ♪

36:05.062 --> 36:09.199
♪ With the air like I don't
care, baby, by the way ♪

36:09.233 --> 36:11.401
♪ <i>Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh,</i>
<i>'cause I'm happy</i> ♪

