in the glee club.

41:51.948 --> 41:53.849
It's a part of all of us.

41:53.884 --> 41:55.418
Of course you're sad about it.

41:55.452 --> 41:57.253
I don't know, Mr. Schue.

41:57.287 --> 41:59.588
With this and Finn,

41:59.623 --> 42:02.458
it's kind of hard
to believe that anything lasts.

42:02.492 --> 42:04.660
I don't have any more pep talks.

42:04.694 --> 42:06.962
I just have you guys.

42:06.997 --> 42:09.465
And the memory
of the people on this wall.

42:11.101 --> 42:13.235
My friends.

42:13.270 --> 42:17.206
I mean, we share
this special bond.

42:17.240 --> 42:19.375
We're the only ones
in the world who-who know

42:19.409 --> 42:20.910
