meant to us.

42:20.944 --> 42:23.145
What it felt like
to sing together.

42:23.180 --> 42:26.749
To be... to be together.

42:26.783 --> 42:30.119
And what it feels like
to say good-bye to it.

42:30.153 --> 42:32.388
