a few days until, uh,

42:53.043 --> 42:55.644
Sue shuts the lights out
on the choir room, so...

42:55.679 --> 42:57.613
let's make the most of them.

43:02.219 --> 43:04.520
I mean, I know we got to
finish our wine first.

43:04.554 --> 43:07.156
Mmm.
But when we do, we cannot let

43:07.190 --> 43:09.325
that glee club go
the way of the dodo.

43:09.359 --> 43:11.827
Oh, couldn't have said it
better myself.

43:11.862 --> 43:14.330
Holly Holliday...

